title: Walk with Me (Rotimi EP)
text: Walk with Me is the second <a href="extended%20play">extended play</a> (EP) by Nigerian-American recording artist <a href="Rotimi%20%28actor%29">Rotimi</a>. The EP was released on May 24, 2019, by FrontRo Music Group and <a href="Empire%20Distribution">Empire Distribution</a>.
